Transnet to Raise Coal-Line Tariffs as Much as 30%, Reuters Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-24T10:39:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/transnet-to-raise-coal-line-tariffs-as-much-as-30-reuters-says.html
Transnet Ltd., the state-owned rail
and transport company, will raise tariffs on the railway line
used to transport coal to the Richards Bay Coal Terminal by 26
percent to 30 percent from March 26, Reuters said, citing
Transnet spokesman Sandile Simelane.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
